sub_title: SOCIAL INNOVATOR 2 LIVE AND LET LIVE!
summary:
THINK: we gotta use what we got to get what we want ! 
Freedom, Healing and Equality!

Guess what ....LOVE - no not Fear - is the Path!

The Dutch Challenge : 
First 
to chase Apartheid from the city of Amsterdam where it has come home to roost after been slain by Madiba in 1994. 
Second 
to join hands for delivering an effective, global education system that generates capable and successful innercity young leadership, with a real shot at social enrichment and success. A system based on the rich and sustained metropolitan diversity teachings! Amsterdam Freedom School awaits being born today. 
Obstacles: our distracted focus; devided interest; abundant greed; lack of boldness; silent poverty and loud unequality. As a glocal innercity freedom organizer focussing on the People part in the P3 equation I love to join talents, skills and intell with global like minded professionals to get the job done and live in a more just world asap, taking the marathon track while also having fun during the proces. We master baby steps while releasing huge amounts of global Inner Gold! Step One: the Marley Kartini Global Community College of 2015! Yesss...Let's go!
